@NODE Introduction
@TITLE "au.player · Introduction"


    @{b}Introduction@{ub}


    au.player is a player plugin for AmiNetRadio (@{" website " system "OpenURL http://anr.amigazeux.net/" })
    which adds support for the Sun/ NeXT Audio format, usually 
    files which end with an ".au" or ".snd" suffix.


    Following subformats are supported currently:

    * 8bit PCM mono/ stereo

    * 16bit PCM mono/ stereo

    * 24bit PCM mono/ stereo

    * 32bit PCM mono/ stereo

    * A-law 

    * µ-law 

    * 32bit IEEE Float

    * 64bit IEEE Float 


    Sun/ NeXT Audio files are usually created in Big Endian format, but
    au.player also supports files which were written in Little Endian
    format (e.g. files created by Audacity, etc.).

@ENDNODE

